    "English": "A lightweight metal product, heavily used in the manufacture of <span class=\"name name-technology\">starship parts</span> and <span class=\"name name-technology\">deployable technology</span>. A mainstay of the construction industries of all known primary species.<br><br>Crafted from <span class=\"name name-earth\">Ferrite Dust</span>.",
